data.description: Embrace modern living in this 4-bed, 3-bath, 2-story home on a spacious corner lot. The kitchen, featuring Corian counters and new stainless steel appliances, opens to a family room with a wood-burning fireplace and a sliding door to the back deck. The expansive primary bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and a 3/4 bathroom. The new carpet throughout.  Enjoy the large backyard with a storage shed. Situated near retail, amenities, and Buckley AFB, this residence harmonizes convenience and serenity. This home invites seamless indoor-outdoor living for a lifestyle of entertaining, as well as comfort and sophistication.
